<item>
            <title>[LU-10966] `lfs check` documentation is misleading</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10966</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;`lfs check` command documentation and arguments are misleading,&lt;br/&gt;
it is used to check targets, not servers, as documentation states (or am I wrong?).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I propose to change man page and add new arguments:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;mdts&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;all&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Proposing patch is in attachment.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
